# Odds Shopper — environment variables
#
# ODDS_API_KEY (optional — enables real-time data from The Odds API)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get a FREE key at https://the-odds-api.com
#   - 500 credits/month, no credit card required
#   - With 30-min caching, personal use stays well under the limit
#     (football season: ~120 credits/month  |  all 6 sports: ~360/month)
#
# When ODDS_API_KEY is set:
#   • Web app (app.py)           → real-time lines, 9 books including Hard Rock
#   • CLI (odds_shopper_pro.py)  → real-time lines, shows credit usage
#
# When NOT set:
#   • Web app falls back to ActionNetwork (free, ~15-30 min delay, 7 books)
#
# To use: copy this file to ".env" and replace the value below.

ODDS_API_KEY=paste_your_key_here
